```
vcs -q -full64 -sverilog -j4 +nospecify +notimingcheck test.sv && timeout 10s ./simv
...
t=  65/02 src=00 dst=00 sent              1
t=  75/03 src=00 dst=00 received          1
test passed!
$finish called from file "test.sv", line 106.
$finish at simulation time                   95
```

What 'verilator' command line do we use to run your example?

```
verilator --binary -Wno-fatal --CFLAGS -fcoroutines -j 8 --top-module tb_ring test.sv && timeout 10s ./obj_dir/Vtb_ring
```

What 'verilator --version' are you using?  Did you try it with the git master version?  Did you try it with other simulators?

```
